### AlphaCopilot API Requests for Insomnia/Postman

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Register User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "testpass123",
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### 2. Login User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "testpass123"
}

### 3. Send Chat Message (requires JWT token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/message
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "content": "Привет! Как дела?",
  "category": "Общее"
}

### 4. Send Business Chat Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/message
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "content": "Помоги составить бизнес-план для стартапа",
  "category": "Бизнес"
}

### 5. Get Chat History (requires JWT token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Health Check (Swagger UI)
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Test Scenarios:

### Invalid Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "wronguser",
  "password": "wrongpass"
}

### Empty Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/message
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "content": "",
  "category": "Общее"
}

### Register Duplicate User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "newpass123",
  "email": "newemail@example.com"
}

### Chat without Authorization
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Тест без токена",
  "category": "Общее"
}